      • validateKeyStore

        public void validateKeyStore(java.io.File keyStoreFile)
                      throws KeyNotFoundException
        Validates the key store file. If it doesnot exist then raises an exception.
        Parameters:
        keyStoreFile - File Key store file to be searched, which will be responsible for encryption.
        Throws:
        KeyNotFoundException - If the keyStoreFile is NULL or it doesn't exist.
